channel.title: Need car suggestions
channel.description: Well, I'm gonna buy a car soon, and I can't decide what to buy, what things should I take into consideration when buying a car? I've looked at Toyota Celica, because it looks good, but other than that I don't know if it's any good. My budget for a car is about 5k €.

item.title: Need car suggestions
item.dc:creator: @imsuperman05 imsuperman05
item.description:
@imsuperman05 wrote:

first figure out what are you going to be looking for in a car, then develop a list of cars that are in your budget and matches what your searching for, then go out and yeah… dont know what else to talk about unless you can say what you are looking for specifically

[/quote]@_@ that car’s ugly as hell.[/quote]En ymmärrä englantia.
